Introduction

Hunter is a Thai singer under KQ Entertainment. He debuted on March 30, 2023, as the main dancer of the boy group Xikers with their first mini album "House of Tricky: Doorbell Ringing"

He was introduced as a member of KQ Fellaz 2 on August 19, 2022 alongside Seeun.

His BT23 team participated in the show Got Talent and took 1st.

He also learned to play golf at the age of 6 and won gold and bronze medals when he was just 10 years old, he won these medals from the 1st CGA & U.S Kids Golf Par 3 Challenge in 2015.
